{"type":"message","id":"c623d3f2","parentId":"2a0aba7f","timestamp":"2026-03-04T00:41:24.774Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了！第一个工具 \"Market News\" (finnhub.news.execute.v1) 看起来最合适。它有84%成功率和921.4ms的平均响应时间。\n\n让我使用这个工具获取新闻。用户要求热度≥80的新闻。让我先看看这个工具返回什么参数，然后执行它。\n\n根据示例，参数是 `{\"category\":\"general\"}`。不过用户要求热度≥80的新闻，我需要看看返回的数据里是否包含热度/相关性指标。\n\n让我先执行看看返回什么数据。","thinkingSignature":"cb187da2c0057416f2a0ce731600236d24b39a625033fb93e01ef2ff4e45f5bc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5zwp6kbg9uda_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/qveris-official/scripts/qveris_tool.mjs execute finnhub.news.execute.v1 --search-id 9c652d82-2642-4832-bef8-e062148ea99a --params '{\"category\":\"general\"}' --max-size 50000","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":6338,"output":201,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20523,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772584877104}}
{"type":"message","id":"19071bd1","parentId":"c623d3f2","timestamp":"2026-03-04T00:41:27.209Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5zwp6kbg9uda_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Success\nTime: 854.96ms | Cost: 6.5\n\nResult:\n{\n  \"status_code\": 200,\n  \"message\": \"Result content is too long (58353 bytes). You can reference the truncated content (50000 bytes) and download the full content from the url provided.\",\n  \"full_content_file_url\": \"http://qveris-tool-results-cache-bj.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/tool_result_cache%2F20260304%2Ffinnhub.news.execute.v1%2Fe6aae1eb98d147aea71ba5d89adbe178.json?OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5tM3qNRZSgSrg1iSTALm&Expires=1772592086&Signature=LYrwwlstee6URORRtCdxAJSdJm4%3D\",\n  \"truncated_content\": \"[{\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772578647, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Sam Altman tells OpenAI staffers that military's 'operational decisions' are up to the government\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580637, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108236135-1764788503612-gettyimages-2197366908-dsc00472_mof5bjgn.jpeg?v=1772572082&w=1920&h=1080\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"CNBC\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"In an all-hands meetings with OpenAI employees on Tuesday, CEO Sam Altman said his company doesn't get to choose how the military uses its technology.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/03/sam-altman-tells-openai-staff-operational-decisions-up-to-government.html\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772568014, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Why stocks moved off their worst levels — plus, a step forward in Honeywell's split\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580568, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108196912-1757519281221-gettyimages-2223423631-20090101250708-99-391116.jpeg?v=1772566560&w=1920&h=1080\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"CNBC\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Every weekday, the Investing Club releases the Homestretch; an actionable afternoon update just in time for the last hour of trading.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/03/why-stocks-moved-off-their-worst-levels-plus-a-step-forward-in-honeywells-split.html\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772566200, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Can Broadcom’s stock break the software curse after earnings? Here’s what Wall Street is saying.\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580562, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Best known for its chip business, Broadcom has seen its stock get weighed down by concerns over exposure to software sales.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/can-broadcoms-stock-break-the-software-curse-after-earnings-heres-what-wall-street-is-saying-e4845949\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772565300, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Get ready for Trump to chicken out on Iran as markets fall and gas prices rise\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580560, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Financial markets are now pricing in months of higher gasoline prices, and panic is spreading.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/get-ready-for-trump-to-chicken-out-on-iran-as-markets-fall-and-gas-prices-rise-52f09fb7\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772564340, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Why Blue Owl’s private-credit shocker has investors seeing shadows of Bear Stearns\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580558, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"This is not yet a repeat of 2008. But dismissing it as a nonevent would be a mistake.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/why-blue-owls-private-credit-shocker-has-investors-seeing-shadows-of-bear-stearns-45506299\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772561280, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Trump says when he’s done with Iran, oil prices will drop even lower than they were before\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580549, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"High oil prices can be expected for “a little while,” President Donald Trump said Tuesday, as he predicted a significant fall for crude when the U.S. operation against Iran ends.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/trump-says-when-hes-done-with-iran-oil-prices-will-drop-even-lower-than-they-were-before-bcfefe9b\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772559360, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Energy investors go stock picking, benefiting Chevron over Exxon\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580539, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Disruption to global energy supplies and the prospect of an ever-widening conflict in the Middle East has sent crude-oil and natural-gas futures higher — and exposed subtle differences on how investors treat the stocks of different energy companies.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/energy-investors-go-stock-picking-benefiting-chevron-over-exxon-bb36de39\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772556120, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Pinterest’s stock is rising. Here’s why investors are cheering a big boost to the buyback program.\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580526, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Pinterest’s new share-repurchase authorization represents nearly a third of the company’s market cap and signals to one analyst that an activist is satisfied with the company’s strategic vision.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/pinterests-stock-is-rising-heres-why-investors-are-cheering-a-big-boost-to-the-buyback-program-e46ab090\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772555951, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"We're exiting a financial already on its way out and adding again to our newest stock\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580530, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108263450-1770660021829-gettyimages-2260237949-US_STOCKS.jpeg?v=1772554502&w=1920&h=1080\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"CNBC\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"These moves are helping us reposition the portfolio with a more defensive tilt, while preserving our sizable cash position.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/03/were-exiting-a-financial-already-on-its-way-out-and-adding-again-to-our-newest-stock.html\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772554680, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Micron and other memory stocks see outsized losses. What’s behind the big moves?\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580509, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Analysts don’t see any negative shift in fundamentals for memory-chip stocks — and UBS offers a new highly upbeat earnings forecast for Micron specifically.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/micron-and-other-memory-stocks-see-outsized-losses-whats-behind-the-big-moves-c14882a0\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772553840, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Investors are now learning a painful lesson: Buying a dip driven by geopolitics isn’t a slam dunk.\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580507, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Investors rushed to buy U.S. stocks on Monday after the U.S. and Israeli bombardment of Iran helped inspire a global selloff. That may have been short-sighted.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/investors-are-now-learning-a-painful-lesson-buying-a-dip-driven-by-geopolitics-isnt-a-slam-dunk-219d6bbe\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772552460, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"These S&P 500 stocks are falling the hardest on Tuesday\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580500, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Stocks of gold miners and computer-memory makers were hit especially hard, while Best Buy led the S&P 500 with a gain after its earnings report.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/these-s-p-500-stocks-are-falling-the-hardest-on-tuesday-bedc2c07\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772549779, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"New York Fed's Williams says tariff burden falls 'overwhelmingly' on U.S. businesses and consumers\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580491, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108229868-1763741665578-108229868-1763730430401-gettyimages-2233025951-WILLIAMS_ECNY.jpeg?v=1772548607&w=1920&h=1080\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"CNBC\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Williams said that not only were the tariffs being felt at home, but they also were keeping the Fed from reaching its 2% inflation goal.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/03/new-york-feds-williams-says-tariff-burden-falls-overwhelmingly-on-us-businesses-and-consumers.html\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\