-over-iran-u-s-stocks-were-mostly-unscathed-heres-why-92dc87c5\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772487960, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Gold just passed its stress test — what happens next will tell investors if they’re right\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580292, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Gold did exactly what it was supposed to after the Iran strike. Is the spike temporary or a new era for the safe-haven trade?\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/gold-just-passed-its-stress-test-what-happens-next-will-tell-investors-if-theyre-right-35de6d2f\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772487600, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Iran conflict unlikely to hurt U.S. economy or boost inflation — but the Fed won’t be quick to cut rates\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580272, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"The U.S. attack on Iran won’t boost U.S. inflation or harm the economy in a major way, analysts say, unless in the unlikely case that the conflict drags on for months and sharply raises the price of oil.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/iran-conflict-unlikely-to-hurt-u-s-economy-or-boost-inflation-but-the-fed-wont-be-quick-to-cut-rates-6e7d315a\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772487180, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Trump’s war on Iran could make many things more expensive, despite his affordability promises\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580273, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"How do you campaign on “affordability” if you just pushed up prices?\\